        {"id": "q7", "type": "fill", "difficulty": 3, "sectionNo": 1, "stem": "一根绳子长24米，剪成4米一段，需要剪______次。", "answer": "5", "score": 10, "solution": "24÷4=6段，剪5次。", "knowledgePoints": ["剪绳子"]},
